msgctxt "56_Hirauchi"
msgid "The speech ended without incident. Did anything crop up on your end?"
msgstr "El discurso terminó sin incidentes. ¿Ha ocurrido algo?"

msgctxt "68_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. Found the guy who was sendin' punks to heckle ya.\\r\n"\n"We had us a little debate."
msgstr "Sí. Encontré al tipo que estaba enviando matones a\\r \n"\n"molestarte. Tuvimos un pequeño debate."

msgctxt "80_Hirauchi"
msgid "Aha, I knew it! He was on Shirakawa's payroll, wasn't he?"
msgstr "¡Ajá, lo sabía! Estaba pagado por Shirakawa, ¿no?"

msgctxt "92_Numai"
msgid "Was he...?"
msgstr "¿Era él...?"

msgctxt "104_Saejima"
msgid "Nah. I thought he was, so I gave 'em the third degree.\\r\n"\n"Turns out he was actin' alone."
msgstr "No. Pensé que lo era, así que lo interrogué en profundidad.\\r\n"\n"Resulta que estaba actuando solo."

msgctxt "116_Hirauchi"
msgid "Oh, I see."
msgstr "Oh, ya veo."

msgctxt "128_Numai"
msgid "What did I tell you, Hirauchi-kun? Don't accuse good men\\r\n"\n"without proof. Do you understand why that is now?"
msgstr "¿Qué te dije, Hirauchi-kun? No acuses a hombres honestos sin\\r \n"\n"pruebas. ¿Entiendes ahora por qué?"

msgctxt "140_Hirauchi"
msgid "Yes, sir. I'm sorry."
msgstr "Sí, señor. Lo siento."

msgctxt "152_Numai"
msgid "Thank you for your help today, Saejima-san. I regret that\\r\n"\n"my position prevents me from offering a token of gratitude."
msgstr "Gracias por su ayuda hoy, Saejima-san. Lamento que\\r\n"\n"mi posición me impide ofrecerle una muestra de gratitud."

msgctxt "164_Saejima"
msgid "Don't mention it. Civic duty and all that."
msgstr "No te preocupes. Es el Deber cívico y todo eso."

msgctxt "176_Hirauchi"
msgid "I really appreciate it, too. Well, goodbye then."
msgstr "Yo también te lo agradezco. Bueno, adiós."

msgctxt "200_Hirauchi"
msgid "Sensei?"
msgstr "¿Señor?"

msgctxt "212_Numai"
msgid "Thank you again, Saejima-san. For everything."
msgstr "Gracias de nuevo, Saejima-san. Por todo."

msgctxt "224_Saejima"
msgid "You bet. Knock 'em dead."
msgstr "De nada, Numai-san, de nada..."

